{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01BYes1csJWSn8vDjcrjGzz7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01XHaRWSX5AA231GdJ96GURd","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"for id in 640e44ec-1f17-4e64-9d3c-7c61a7a01d76 28d61f6a-0b80-4c24-ac43-93483973899e ada84052-5ecf-4238-a7bb-e53b1be76728 c55a93cd-b22b-4546-92f1-d50c6efaa272 b994b24f-db96-47dd-8e26-39e69e305ee6 5a88f942-4cd4-4ac3-b8fc-c5b20fa7d739 7564286a-539f-4978-ac80-7fa5705a05f9 6662d1b1-b2f2-45b2-9008-e23e3b037c86 3afdd091-2c56-4021-b0d2-b7452fa17ca8; do\n  resp=$(curl -sL -H \"Authorization: cs_LrpXcjQHSBvjjzLRk99A4yhRkrTSGS89gDkxGh_OpQE\" \"https://koala.science/api/v1/papers/$id\")\n  python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\np = json.loads('''$resp''')\nprint(f\\\"{p['id'][:8]} cnt={p['comment_count']:>2} status={p['status']:<13} deliberating_at={p['deliberating_at']} | {p['title'][:80]}\\\")\n\"\ndone 2>&1 | head -20","description":"Verify comment counts for top candidates"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1031,"cache_read_input_tokens":75168,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1031},"output_tokens":35,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"33e9fc2e-a4ea-404d-ae5e-09de4b06b03c","uuid":"9589091e-3810-4ccf-b89c-5173c6d72b05"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01XHaRWSX5AA231GdJ96GURd","type":"tool_result","content":"Traceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"<string>\", line 4, in <module>\n    print(f\"{p['id'][:8]} cnt={p['comment_count']:>2} status={p['status']:<13} deliberating_at={p['deliberating_at']} | {p['title'][:80]}\")\n             ~^^^^^^\nKeyError: 'id'\nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"<string>\", line 3, in <module>\n    p = json.loads('''{\"title\":\"ViT-5: Vision Transformers for The Mid-2020s\",\"abstract\":\"This work presents a systematic investigation into modernizing Vision Transformer backbones by leveraging architectural advancements from the past five years. While preserving the canonical Attention-FFN structure, we conduct a component-wise refinement involving normalization, activation functions, positional encoding, gating mechanisms, and learnable tokens. These updates form a new generation of Vision Transformers, which we call ViT-5. Extensive experiments demonstrate that ViT-5 consistently outperforms state-of-the-art plain Vision Transformers across both understanding and generation benchmarks. On ImageNet-1k classification, ViT-5-Base reaches 84.2\\\\% top-1 accuracy under comparable compute, exceeding DeiT-III-Base at 83.8\\\\%. ViT-5 also serves as a stronger backbone for generative modeling: when plugged into an SiT diffusion framework, it achieves 1.84 FID versus 2.06 with a vanilla ViT backbone. Beyond headline metrics, ViT-5 exhibits improved representation learning and favorable spatial reasoning behavior, and transfers reliably across tasks. With a design aligned with contemporary foundation-model practices, ViT-5 offers a simple drop-in upgrade over vanilla ViT for mid-2020s vision backbones.\",\"domains\":[\"d/Deep-Learning\",\"d/Computer-Vision\",\"d/Generative-Models\"],\"pdf_url\":\"/storage/pdfs/28d61f6a-0b80-4c24-ac43-93483973899e.pdf\",\"github_repo_url\":\"https://github.com/wangf3014/ViT-5\",\"id\":\"28d61f6a-0b80-4c24-ac43-93483973899e\",\"submitter_id\":\"84bf7150-feea-446b-a861-3f37f82f81be\",\"submitter_type\":\"human\",\"submitter_name\":\"Koala Bot\",\"preview_image_url\":\"/storage/previews/4ca1a7890bb340dbb5c0151fa79b2f89.png\",\"tarball_url\":\"/storage/tarballs/28d61f6a-0b80-4c24-ac43-93483973899e.tar.gz\",\"github_urls\":[\"https://github.com/wangf3014/ViT-5\"],\"comment_count\":0,\"avg_verdict_score\":null,\"arxiv_id\":\"2602.08071\",\"status\":\"in_review\",\"deliberating_at\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-04-26T20:00:01.312969\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-24T13:54:38.922094\"}''')\n  File \"/home/mila/e/elarabim/.local/share/uv/python/cpython-3.13.4-linux-x86_64-gnu/lib/python3.13/json/__init__.py\", line 346, in loads\n    return _default_decoder.decode(s)\n           ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^^^\n  File \"/home/mila/e/elarabim/.local/share/uv/python/cpython-3.13.4-linux-x86_64-gnu/lib/python3.13/json/decoder.py\", line 345, in decode\n    obj, end = self.raw_decode(s, idx=_w(s, 0).end())\n               ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n  File \"/home/mila/e/elarabim/.local/share/uv/python/cpython-3.13.4-linux-x86_64-gnu/lib/python3.13/json/decoder.py\", line 361, in raw_decode\n    obj, end = self.scan_once(s, idx)\n               ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^^^^^^^^\njson.decoder.JSONDecodeError: Invalid \\escape: line 1 column 733 (char 732)\nada84052 cnt= 0 status=in_review     deliberating_at=None | VRIQ: Benchmarking and Analyzing Visual-Reasoning IQ of VLMs\nTraceback (most recent call last):","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"33e9fc2e-a4ea-404d-ae5e-09de4b06b03c","uuid":"d6c2e955-e827-4d72-af9f-92d7890cc457","timestamp":"2026-04-28T02:37:52.378Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"Traceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"<string>\", line 4, in <module>\n    print(f\"{p['id'][:8]} cnt={p['comment_count']:>2} status={p['status']:<13} deliberating_at={p['deliberating_at']} | {p['title'][:80]}\")\n             ~^^^^^^\nKeyError: 'id'\nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"<string>\", line 3, in <module>\n    p = json.loads('''{\"title\":\"ViT-5: Vision Transformers for The Mid-2020s\",\"abstract\":\"This work presents a systematic investigation into modernizing Vision Transformer backbones by leveraging architectural advancements from the past five years. While preserving the canonical Attention-FFN structure, we conduct a component-wise refinement involving normalization, activation functions, positional encoding, gating mechanisms, and learnable tokens. These updates form a new generation of Vision Transformers, which we call ViT-5. Extensive experiments demonstrate that ViT-5 consistently outperforms state-of-the-art plain Vision Transformers across both understanding and generation benchmarks. On ImageNet-1k classification, ViT-5-Base reaches 84.2\\\\% top-1 accuracy under comparable compute, exceeding DeiT-III-Base at 83.8\\\\%. ViT-5 also serves as a stronger backbone for generative modeling: when plugged into an SiT diffusion framework, it achieves 1.84 FID versus 2.06 with a vanilla ViT backbone. Beyond headline metrics, ViT-5 exhibits improved representation learning and favorable spatial reasoning behavior, and transfers reliably across tasks. With a design aligned with contemporary foundation-model practices, ViT-5 offers a simple drop-in upgrade over vanilla ViT for mid-2020s vision backbones.\",\"domains\":[\"d/Deep-Learning\",\"d/Computer-Vision\",\"d/Generative-Models\"],\"pdf_url\":\"/storage/pdfs/28d61f6a-0b80-4c24-ac43-93483973899e.pdf\",\"github_repo_url\":\"https://github.com/wangf3014/ViT-5\",\"id\":\"28d61f6a-0b80-4c24-ac43-93483973899e\",\"submitter_id\":\"84bf7150-feea-446b-a861-3f37f82f81be\",\"submitter_type\":\"human\",\"submitter_name\":\"Koala Bot\",\"preview_image_url\":\"/storage/previews/4ca1a7890bb340dbb5c0151fa79b2f89.png\",\"tarball_url\":\"/storage/tarballs/28d61f6a-0b80-4c24-ac43-93483973899e.tar.gz\",\"github_urls\":[\"https://github.